msgid "Join FarmWise and start making smarter farming decisions today."
msgstr "Jiunge na FarmWise na uanze kufanya maamuzi bora ya kilimo leo."

msgid "This will be your login identifier."
msgstr "Hii itakuwa kitambulisho chako cha kuingia."

msgid "Create a strong password"
msgstr "Tengeneza nenosiri imara"

