# ─── Home page ───
msgid "Iringa Region Farming Advisor"
msgstr "Mshauri wa Kilimo wa Mkoa wa Iringa"

msgid "Built for Iringa Region Farmers"
msgstr "Imejengwa kwa Wakulima wa Mkoa wa Iringa"

msgid "Grow Smarter,"
msgstr "Kua kwa Akili,"

msgid "Harvest Better"
msgstr "Vuna Vizuri Zaidi"

msgid "A free advisory tool for farmers in Iringa Region, Tanzania. Register your location, pick the crops you grow — Maize, Irish Potatoes, Onions, Avocado, Wheat, and more — and receive planting and harvest guidance matched to Iringa's highland seasons."
msgstr "Zana ya bure ya ushauri kwa wakulima wa Mkoa wa Iringa, Tanzania. Sajili eneo lako, chagua mazao unayolima — Mahindi, Viazi vya Ulaya, Vitunguu, Parachichi, Ngano, na zaidi — na upokee mwongozo wa kupanda na kuvuna unaofaa na misimu ya milima ya Iringa."

msgid "Get Started Free"
msgstr "Anza Bure"

msgid "Serving Iringa Region farmers"
msgstr "Kutumikia wakulima wa Mkoa wa Iringa"

msgid "Iringa Region, Tanzania"
msgstr "Mkoa wa Iringa, Tanzania"

msgid "Good Morning, Farmer"
msgstr "Habari za Asubuhi, Mkulima"

msgid "Your Farm Overview"
msgstr "Muhtasari wa Shamba Lako"

msgid "Current Weather"
msgstr "Hali ya Hewa Sasa"

msgid "Partly Cloudy"
msgstr "Mawingu Kidogo"

msgid "Active Crops"
msgstr "Mazao Yanayoendelea"

msgid "+2 this month"
msgstr "+2 mwezi huu"

msgid "Harvest Ready"
msgstr "Tayari Kuvuna"

msgid "Within 2 weeks"
msgstr "Ndani ya wiki 2"

msgid "Plant Now!"
msgstr "Panda Sasa!"

msgid "Why FarmWise"
msgstr "Kwa Nini FarmWise"

msgid "Everything You Need to Farm Smarter"
msgstr "Kila Kitu Unachohitaji Kulima kwa Akili"

msgid "Powerful tools and real-time data to help you make the best decisions for your farm, from planting to harvest."
msgstr "Zana zenye nguvu na data ya wakati halisi kukusaidia kufanya maamuzi bora kwa shamba lako, kutoka upandaji hadi uvunaji."

msgid "Location-Based Forecasts"
msgstr "Utabiri Kulingana na Eneo"

msgid "Set your farm location within Iringa Region and receive accurate, hyper-local weather data powered by Open-Meteo — tuned to Iringa's highland elevation and unimodal rainfall season."
msgstr "Weka eneo la shamba lako ndani ya Mkoa wa Iringa na upokee data sahihi ya hali ya hewa ya eneo lako kupitia Open-Meteo — iliyorekebishwa kwa urefu wa milima ya Iringa na msimu wa mvua."

msgid "Weather-Smart Advisories"
msgstr "Ushauri Unaotegemea Hali ya Hewa"

msgid "Receive timely warnings about extreme weather, frost risk, and optimal planting windows. Never get caught off guard by unpredictable conditions again."
msgstr "Pokea onyo la mapema kuhusu hali mbaya ya hewa, hatari ya theluji, na nyakati bora za kupanda. Usishtushwe tena na hali zisizotarajiwa."

msgid "Regional Crop Calendar"
msgstr "Kalenda ya Mazao ya Mkoa"

msgid "Browse a curated library of crops grown in Iringa Region — Maize, Wheat, Irish Potatoes, Onions, Avocado, Common Beans, Sunflower, Tomatoes, and more — with planting and harvest windows matched to Iringa's long-rains season (November–April)."
msgstr "Vinjari mkusanyiko wa mazao yanayolimwa Mkoa wa Iringa — Mahindi, Ngano, Viazi vya Ulaya, Vitunguu, Parachichi, Maharagwe ya kawaida, Alizeti, Nyanya, na zaidi — na nyakati za kupanda na kuvuna zinazolingana na msimu wa mvua wa Iringa (Novemba–Aprili)."

msgid "Track Your Crops"
msgstr "Fuatilia Mazao Yako"

msgid "Build your personal crop list and monitor planting and harvest statuses at a glance. Keep your farm organized and always know what needs attention next."
msgstr "Jenga orodha yako ya mazao na ufuatilie hali ya upandaji na uvunaji kwa haraka. Weka shamba lako likiwa na mpangilio na ujue daima kinachohitaji umakini."

msgid "Early Warnings"
msgstr "Onyo la Mapema"

msgid "Get proactive alerts for weather events that could affect your crops. Stay ahead of storms, droughts, and temperature extremes with advance notice."
msgstr "Pata tahadhari za mapema kwa hali za hewa zinazoweza kuathiri mazao yako. Kuwa tayari kwa dhoruba, ukame, na joto kali kwa taarifa ya mapema."

msgid "Simple Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashibodi Rahisi"

msgid "Everything at a glance. Your dashboard shows weather, crop statuses, and advisories in one clean view. No complicated menus, just the information you need."
msgstr "Kila kitu kwa mtazamo mmoja. Dashibodi yako inaonyesha hali ya hewa, hali za mazao, na ushauri katika muonekano mmoja. Hakuna menyu ngumu, tu taarifa unazohitaji."

msgid "Quick Setup"
msgstr "Usanidi wa Haraka"

msgid "Up and Running in 3 Steps"
msgstr "Anza kwa Hatua 3"

msgid "From sign-up to personalized advisories in under two minutes."
msgstr "Kutoka usajili hadi ushauri ulioboreshwa kwa chini ya dakika mbili."

msgid "Create Your Account"
msgstr "Fungua Akaunti Yako"

msgid "Sign up in seconds with just a username and password. No email verification required."
msgstr "Jisajili kwa sekunde chache kwa jina la mtumiaji na nenosiri tu. Hakuna uthibitisho wa barua pepe unaohitajika."

msgid "Set Your Location"
msgstr "Weka Eneo Lako"

msgid "Search for your village, ward, or town within Iringa Region. We connect to local weather data for your exact farm location instantly."
msgstr "Tafuta kijiji, kata, au mji wako ndani ya Mkoa wa Iringa. Tunaunganisha mara moja na data ya hali ya hewa ya mahali pa shamba lako."

msgid "Pick Your Crops"
msgstr "Chagua Mazao Yako"

msgid "Browse the crop library, add what you grow, and start receiving tailored planting and harvest guidance."
msgstr "Vinjari maktaba ya mazao, ongeza unayolima, na uanze kupokea mwongozo ulioboreshwa wa kupanda na kuvuna."

msgid "Ready to Grow Smarter?"
msgstr "Uko Tayari Kulima kwa Akili Zaidi?"

msgid "Made for farmers in Iringa Region, Tanzania. Get personalized crop and weather guidance tailored to your highland farm — completely free."
msgstr "Imetengenezwa kwa wakulima wa Mkoa wa Iringa, Tanzania. Pata mwongozo wa mazao na hali ya hewa ulioboreshwa kwa shamba lako la milima — bure kabisa."

msgid "Create Free Account"
msgstr "Fungua Akaunti Bure"

